"Don't argue with me, Roger" said the figure. At that point both crews couldn't figure out who or what was that figure cloaked in blue. Slowly the light started to go away and they were able to see it clearly. It was the famous known Pythonelly. One of the oldest wizard ever knew. Pythonelly came to them in order to to give a message. Pythonelly looked at Poor Henry and said " Poor Henry, you have a biggest quest than just fighting this fools". Roger rolled his eyes, while Pythonelly continue talking, "You have to keep your journey and find the Book of Many Faces. This books will bring knowledge and recognognition. Instead of finding, get this people to help you! I come with tree gifts, that will help you to get achieve your quest faster!"
